{"tid":2179184,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"我推個仔(推しの子)真係好能好睇...","createTime":"2020-08-29T02:40:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T11:56:31.000Z","uid":105678,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"12720a7f2f65fd215c92e3aeab81b0e63984a13b","tid":2179184,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T02:40:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2o0HhO8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2o0HhO8.jpg&h=db14359e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原作係「輝夜姬」作者嘅赤坂アカ<br />\n<br />\n第一集即刻超展開，本身以為噱頭嘢，之後會無聊<br />\n<br />\n點知一集集都有神轉折，下下都估作者唔到...<br />\n<br />\n女主(男主個妹)性格又吸引，為繼承老母夢想努力，有啲喊位不得不落淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n男主有少少頭腦但行事周密，劇情迷團一個接一個，睇完一集就想睇一下集<br />\n<br />\n仲要作畫係由「你是的淫蕩女王」個作者横槍擔當，畫風夢幻而不失細膩，再加埋男女主遺傳老母對星星眼，型到濕...<br />\n<br />\n結論：好能好睇快啲睇"},{"pid":"a3d99facb6884f60691c692bb6cf2928e4b8587c","tid":2179184,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T02:42:44.000Z","msg":"套野都幾好睇<br />\n作畫又唔錯"},{"pid":"7ebb46d56ff8b0c417f3e2e847e824ab9b84f63a","tid":2179184,"uid":63697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T02:46:22.000Z","msg":"諗起ib 作者本身都寫開呢啲胃痛風<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06f147e7db79dac99405c1a8aef0c275be2a4919","tid":2179184,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ebb46d56ff8b0c417f3e2e847e824ab9b84f63a","tid":2179184,"uid":63697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T02:46:22.000Z","msg":"諗起ib 作者本身都寫開呢啲胃痛風<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T02:56:23.000Z","msg":"Ib都好能好睇，可惜畀人斬咗<br />\n<br />\n今次作畫嘅橫槍本身都係呢類作者，兩位算係一拍即合"},{"pid":"2ec80516136e3005610ccdc2b39f339eca991af4","tid":2179184